      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·王風·006.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">兔爰.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>有兔爰爰，雉離于羅。我生之初，尚無為。我生之後，逢此百罹，尚寐無吪？</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>There is the hare! that which leads it is the snare.
When my king has no proper business,
Why should he reduce us all to such extremity?
He who called us to it, — from him shall come no good.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
