        <seg>有兔爰爰，雉離于罦。我生之初，尚無造。我生之後，逢此百憂，尚寐無覺？</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>There is the hare! in the midst of the snare.
When my king has no proper business,
